snippet.title: Super Mario Bros. CD - Trailer 1
snippet.description:
A trailer for Super Mario Bros. CD, a MSU-1 based SMW rom hack! The trailer features gamplay running on Super NES hardware using the SD2SNES (FXPak Pro) hardware! Please note that there is a low chance things will be exactly the same in subsequent trailers/demos or the final release.

Music by our team member Reski!:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjui9eF2mL4jGmAKVhjvg_g

Contact Us:
https://discord.gg/wpSGt5aTuw
support@famicomcd.org

Check FamicomCD out on Twitter, Tumblr, and our website:
https://twitter.com/FamicomCD
https://www.tumblr.com/famicomcd
https://famicomcd.org

And check out the SMWC3 thread here:
https://www.smwcentral.net/?p=viewthread&t=126918
